sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User<br/>(kubectl/oc)
    participant API as Kubernetes API Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant MutatingWH as CodeFlare Mutating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+ mTLS
    participant ValidatingWH as CodeFlare Validating Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+ mTLS
    participant Controller as RayCluster Controller<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    participant KubeRay as KubeRay Operator
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>OAuth Proxy + Dashboard
    participant Browser as User Browser
    participant Ingress as Ingress/Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+

    Note over User,KubeRay: Flow 1: User Creates RayCluster

    User->>API: Create RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    API->>MutatingWH: POST /mutate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>mTLS (API Server cert)
    MutatingWH-->>API: Inject OAuth proxy + mTLS init containers
    API->>ValidatingWH: POST /validate-ray-io-v1-raycluster<br/>mTLS (API Server cert)
    ValidatingWH-->>API: Validation success
    API-->>User: RayCluster created

    Controller->>API: Watch RayCluster events<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>Controller: RayCluster created event
    Controller->>API: Create Secrets (CA, OAuth TLS)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create Services (Head, Worker)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create ServiceAccount (OAuth)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create NetworkPolicies<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Controller->>API: Create Ingress/Route<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    KubeRay->>API: Watch RayCluster CR
    API-->>KubeRay: RayCluster created event
    KubeRay->>API: Create Ray Head Pod<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    KubeRay->>API: Create Ray Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over Browser,OAuth: Flow 2: User Accesses Ray Dashboard

    Browser->>Ingress: GET https://{raycluster}.{domain}<br/>TLS 1.2+ (no auth)
    Ingress->>HeadPod: Forward to OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    HeadPod->>OAuth: Validate OAuth token<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>Auth: OAuth client credentials
    OAuth-->>HeadPod: Token valid (user identity)
    HeadPod->>HeadPod: Proxy to Ray Dashboard<br/>8080/TCP HTTP (localhost)
    HeadPod-->>Browser: Dashboard HTML

    Note over User,Controller: Flow 3: AppWrapper Job Submission (with Kueue)

    User->>API: Create AppWrapper CR<br/>Auth: User credentials
    API->>MutatingWH: POST /mutate-workload-codeflare-dev-v1beta2-appwrapper<br/>mTLS
    MutatingWH-->>API: Mutation success
    API->>ValidatingWH: POST /validate-workload-codeflare-dev-v1beta2-appwrapper<br/>mTLS
    ValidatingWH-->>API: Validation success
    API-->>User: AppWrapper created

    Controller->>API: Watch AppWrapper events<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>Controller: AppWrapper created event
    Controller->>API: Create Kueue Workload CR<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    API-->>Controller: Workload admitted by Kueue
    Controller->>API: Deploy wrapped resources<br/>ServiceAccount Token
